      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Salesforce Dashboards & Client-Centered Operations</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-3 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 space-y-2">
        <li>Built a management dashboard for weekly metrics and a "home base" view — open vs. closed cases (daily, weekly, monthly), oldest cases, with filters by component, account, and case owner.</li>
